most filler is removed in favor of giving skills more interesting effects when leveling them up!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each run is unique, with each room presenting various risks and rewards!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Acquire relics to aid you in various ways throughout your playthrough, modifying the behavior of your abilities and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on a boss fight that awaits you in the final area of every zone. Each boss has their own special attacks and abilities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many elemental skills interact with each other. For example, some Water skills make puddles, and Storm abilities electrify them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become stronger between runs through meta upgrades in the form of a skill tree!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Conquest Begins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212410/4cd906abe9ab32feb5d46651e7672a12d4503dd2.jpg"},{"name":"Rock and Stone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212410/fa5477582838ac37eb1c6355b0aa25da2b9e1b3e.jpg"},{"name":"Spirit in the Sky","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212410/01dcae32d22b61d0008af839f21ebae6bd14fb2b.jpg"},{"name":"Wait, are we the bad guys?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212410/e4d605a4fa153bc35a6e8c77758cde641e5d5def.jpg"},{"name":"The Spirit of Death","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212410/812ac57bc2d9212d210b5be396efc71aeeeb6f65.jpg"},{"name":"Discipline","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212410/f62f7a52c2f8e55cf6abdf82a3c8a422b7ea9616.jpg"},{"name":"Materialistic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2212410/360dc67a09b84bf66d8b0b1622bef5b908ded8e3.jpg"},{"name":"Shadowkin 